# Markdown extractor demo

This is a `.ssc` Markdown file containing fence blocks.

```lark
// type: Int
let x = 42 in x + 1
```

Some prose between blocks.

```ssc0
def double = (x) => #i.mul(x, 2)
def main = () => #io.print(#i->str(double(21)))
```

End of file.
